[3:21 PM, 5/19/2026] Mani Anna♥️: # 🚀 Full Stack DevOps Project with Jenkins, Docker & Monitoring

This project demonstrates a complete DevOps workflow with CI/CD using Jenkins, containerization using Docker, and monitoring using Prometheus & Grafana.

---

## 📌 Project Overview

This is a simple full-stack application:

* Backend → Node.js + Express  
* Frontend → Nginx (Static HTML)  
* CI/CD → Jenkins Pipeline  
* Containerization → Docker & Docker Compose  
* Monitoring → Prometheus + Grafana + cAdvisor  

