## ⚙️ Features

✔️ Backend API running on Node.js  
✔️ Frontend served using Nginx  
✔️ Multi-container setup using Docker Compose  
✔️ Jenkins CI/CD Pipeline automation  
✔️ Docker Hub image push  
✔️ Monitoring using Prometheus  
✔️ Visualization using Grafana  
✔️ Container metrics using cAdvisor  

---

## 🔄 Jenkins CI/CD Pipeline

Jenkins automatically performs:

1️⃣ Pull code from GitHub  
2️⃣ Build Docker images  
3️⃣ Push images to Docker Hub  
4️⃣ Deploy containers using Docker Compose  

